column5: A Musky from shore? great job on the nice looking fish..
right on man, you got your pic back...nice fish
Great fish.  You must be happy that you got your pic back.  Did you catch him in rapids or slack water?
Those northern skis are gorgeous.  Nice fish.  Must've been a battle from shore like that.

We had stopped for lunch on a large rock in middl of rapids. Caught him in a pool and he imediately went out of pool and down into fast water. Once he got into fast water he didn't like it any more than I and kept tring to get back up into pool, but when I put pressure on him...back to the fast water. Lots of fun!!
Nice fish!  Glad to see the 'missing' pic alive and well.  Thanks for posting it!
Very healthy looking Musky. Thanks for sharing.
